title: Democracy: the Opportunity for Non-Violent Change (vegan / vegans / veganism).
description: In this video I'm speaking with Adriane Gilbert, a vegan activist from Southern Ontario.  At the time of the interview, she was 18 years old and had been vegan for less than a year.  You can find her on instagram, here: https://www.instagram.com/adriane__gilbert/
